oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: White County Post Office
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white photograph of employees at the White County Post Office in Sparta, Tennessee. The men shown are: Bill Williams; John Williams; John Elrod; Robert Cantrell; Mr. Upton; Charlie Meek; Sam Parker; John Elrod and Urban Jarvis.
